nciscaine au Canada.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 7aHISTORY / Canada / General.2bisacsh1 aAnderson, Emma, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBerry, Lynn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBerthiaume, Pierre, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBroué, Catherine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCodignola, Luca, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDanel, Jean-Jacques, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDerome, Robert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDeslandres, Dominique, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDompnier, Bernard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDoyon, Stéphane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDubois, Paul-André, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDubois, Paul-André, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aDufaux, François, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGallat-Morin, Élisabeth, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHébert, Bruno, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJohnston, A.J.B., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKaupp, Dorothée, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKellman, Jordan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLaberge, Alain, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLachance, Matthieu, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLaperrière, Guy, econtributor.4ctb4